<h1>About Us</h1>

<p>Pulse is an open source JavaScript graphics engine built by the <a href="http://onmodulus.com">Modulus</a> team. It offers developers a simple framework to build HTML5 games, requiring only a few lines of JavaScript and a bit of HTML. It even has a simple to use plugin architecture allowing you to easily extend the core functionality.</p>

<p>Here are a few things Pulse will give you:</p>
<ul id="feature-list">
  <li>All the object types you need to build a game (sprites, scenes, etc.)</li>
  <li>HTML5 Canvas engine that is efficient yet powerful</li>
  <li>Support for sprite sheets and animations</li>
  <li>Asset Management done right</li>
  <li>Event manager that supports touch events</li>
  <li>Plugin architecture that is simple to use</li>
  <li>Open source so you can modify and share it however you want</li>
</ul>

